Step into a world where
the future of health care

isn't just a distant dream,
but a reality waiting for you.

I'm Serena Yeung, Assistant
Professor of Biomedical Data
Science.

And an instructor for an
Innovative Health and AI

on campus program
happening in April 2024.

Transforming healthcare through
big data, analytics, and AI

is your opportunity to
break barriers and reshape
the landscape of health care.

Get ready to strategically
integrate technology

into your practice, lead
with disruptive insights,

and foster innovation that
goes beyond the ordinary.

With lectures hands on
experiences, real world

applications, and
networking opportunities.

You'll embark on a
journey to becoming

a leader driving organizational
success in health care.

Secure your spot today and join
us from April 8th to 11th 2024.

Be at the forefront of
healthcare's innovation
evolution.

We hope you'll join us
on the Stanford campus.
